ate the potential data rate, power consumption,\nand array gain capabilities for THz communications. As a roadmap of THz hybrid\nbeamforming design, multiple open problems and potential research directions\nare elaborated.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 21 Jan 2021 07:11:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-06"}
